# ─── acpx_auto_tester agent runtime ─────────────────────────────
# All agent runtime files (campaign state, locks, dispatcher logs,
# per-issue state.json / attempt_state.json / log/ / summary.md) live
# under ifp-result/ and must NEVER be committed.
#
# The ONLY exception is each issue's output directory
# `ifp-result/issue-<iid>/hulat-spec-issue<iid>/`, which the agent
# explicitly force-adds via `git add -f` in stage_and_guard.sh —
# that bypasses this gitignore for the single allowed path.
ifp-result/

# ─── Common local noise ─────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
